| Layer         | Technology                                                   |
|---------------|--------------------------------------------------------------|
| Backend       | Python 3.12 / FastAPI / SQLAlchemy (async)                  |
| Database      | PostgreSQL 16 (Docker volume `pgdata`)                      |
