| AI            | Claude API (Haiku for parsing, Sonnet for intelligence)     |
| Hosting       | DigitalOcean droplet — 104.248.191.152                      |
| Reverse Proxy | Caddy 2 (auto HTTPS)                                        |
| Deployment    | Docker Compose (app + postgres + caddy containers)          |
| Logging       | Loguru — NEVER use print()                                  |
| Linting       | Ruff + pre-commit hooks                                     |
| Testing       | pytest + pytest-asyncio                                     |
| Notifications | Microsoft Teams webhooks (role-specific alert channels)     |
| ERP           | Acctivate (SQL Server, live read-only connection)           |

