## 3. PROJECT STRUCTURE

```
availai/
├── main.py                      # App startup only (~50 lines max)
├── config.py                    # Pydantic settings from env vars
├── database.py                  # SQLAlchemy session factory
├── STABLE.md                    # Registry of critical/stable files — check before refactoring
├── CHANGELOG.md                 # All changes logged here
├── CLAUDE.md                    # Claude Code instructions (mirrors this file)
├── requirements.txt             # Exact-pinned dependencies
├── .pre-commit-config.yaml      # Ruff auto-lint on commit
├── .github/workflows/ci.yml     # Auto test + lint on push
├── alembic/                     # Migrations — DDL changes LIVE HERE ONLY
├── models/                      # SQLAlchemy models — one file per entity
├── schemas/                     # Pydantic request/response models
├── routers/                     # THIN — validate → call service → return
├── services/                    # FAT — all business logic lives here
├── connectors/                  # Vendor API clients (Mouser, DigiKey, etc.)
├── specs/                       # Plain-English business rule contracts
├── tests/                       # pytest — mirrors services/ structure
├── test_fixtures/               # Realistic sample JSON data
└── static/                      # app.js, crm.js, CSS
    └── templates/index.html     # Single-page Jinja2 template
```

### Core Services (always be aware of these)
- `services/sourcing.py` — Multi-source vendor search aggregation
- `services/scoring.py` — Sighting scoring (price 30%, reliability 25%, lead time 20%, geography 15%, terms 10%)
- `services/engagement_scoring.py` — Vendor engagement score (5 behavioral factors)
- `services/routing.py` — Buyer routing, 4-factor scoring
- `services/ownership.py` — Customer ownership, 30-day inactivity rules
- `services/email_service.py` — Microsoft Graph API (batch RFQ, inbox poll, AI parse)
- `services/acctivate_sync.py` — ERP sync (read-only SQL Server)
- `services/scheduler.py` — Background jobs (inbox scan, stock import, mining)

### Key Vendor Connectors
Mouser, DigiKey, OEMSecrets, BrokerBin, Element14, Nexar/Octopart, NetComponents

