## 10. GIT SOURCE-OF-TRUTH WORKFLOW (LIVE SAFETY)

- `main` is the deploy/source-of-truth branch for AVAIL live updates.
- At the end of each coding session, ensure all completed work is pushed and merged to `main`.
- Verify before handoff: `git status` clean, branch is `main`, and `origin/main` matches local `HEAD`.
- Keep files organized in existing AVAIL structure (`app/`, `tests/`, `alembic/`, `scripts/`, `docs/`) so runtime and tooling discover the correct code paths.
- Always provide one copy-paste deploy command after merge/push so live rollout uses the latest `main`.
